{
  "id": "69cf9e47eef7b30ac9117a8b",
  "title": "あり・なり・めり・けり・たり",
  "created": 1775214154,
  "updated": 1775215042,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69cf9e47eef7b30ac9117a8b",
      "text": "あり・なり・めり・けり・たり",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214154,
      "updated": 1775214284
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf9e4900000000009eae80",
      "text": "古典の助動詞など",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214154,
      "updated": 1775214175
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf9e5f00000000009eae82",
      "text": "\t音あり（ねあり）→なり？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214175,
      "updated": 1775214287
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf9ed100000000009eae85",
      "text": "\tにあり→なり？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214289,
      "updated": 1775214355
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf9f1200000000009eae87",
      "text": "\t成り（なり）？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214355,
      "updated": 1775214363
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf9e6f00000000009eae83",
      "text": "\t目あり（めあり）→めり？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214191,
      "updated": 1775214289
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf9e7900000000009eae84",
      "text": "\t来（き）あり→けり？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214202,
      "updated": 1775214612
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa01600000000009eae89",
      "text": "\t\t気あり→けり　じゃないんだ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214615,
      "updated": 1775214641
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa05900000000009eae8b",
      "text": "\tてあり→たり？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214682,
      "updated": 1775214682
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa08400000000009eae8c",
      "text": " \t> 「たり」の原形は「万葉‐八九七」の「老いに弖阿留(テアル) 吾が身の上に 病(やまひ)をと 加へ弖阿礼(テアレ)ば」などの「てあり」であるが、その「て」については、接続助詞とするほか、助動詞「つ」の連用形が接続助詞に転じたもの、また「つ」の連用形そのものとする説がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214724,
      "updated": 1775214726
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf9e5200000000009eae81",
      "text": "  https://kotobank.jp/word/たり-563266#w-2041989",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214163,
      "updated": 1775214732
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa08c00000000009eae8e",
      "text": "  まずそこで揉めるんかい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214733,
      "updated": 1775214750
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa08a00000000009eae8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214730,
      "updated": 1775214730
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa18700000000009eae91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214984,
      "updated": 1775214984
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa16c00000000009eae8f",
      "text": "ぼんやりと使われていたんだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214957,
      "updated": 1775214982
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa19600000000009eae93",
      "text": "\tとなると意味を分析するには膨大なデータを集めて分析する必要がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214998,
      "updated": 1775215037
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa1bd00000000009eae94",
      "text": "\t\t面倒くさそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775215037,
      "updated": 1775215042
    },
    {
      "id": "69cfa18500000000009eae90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775214982,
      "updated": 1775214982
    }
  ]
}